@startuml
!theme plain
actor User
participant Browser
participant FastAPI
participant "Desktop App" as App
participant "Pose\nDetector" as PD
database DBs

== 1. LOGIN & LAUNCH ==

User -> Browser: Open site & login
Browser -> FastAPI: POST /api/auth/login
FastAPI --> Browser: OK + username
User -> Browser: Click "Start Exercise"
FastAPI -> App: subprocess launch
App -> App: Tkinter GUI opens

== 2. EXERCISE SESSION ==

App -> PD: Init poseDetector
loop Every frame
  App -> PD: findPose() + findPosition()
  PD --> App: Landmarks & angles
  App -> App: Smooth angles + exercise logic\n(rep count, form check, overlay)
end
User -> App: Press 'q' to stop

== 3. SAVE & CALCULATE ==

App -> DBs: Save exercise log (spor_db)
App -> DBs: Fetch user weight (user_db)
App -> App: MET-based calorie burn + BMR
App -> DBs: Save to calorie_db
App -> User: Show result (reps + kcal)

== 4. AI COACH (OPTIONAL) ==

User -> App: Open AI Coach
App -> DBs: Collect profile + all logs
App -> App: Generate rule-based report
App -> User: Show report
User -> App: Chat with Coach (via Ollama)
App -> DBs: Collect live data
App -> FastAPI: POST /api/ai-coach/chat
FastAPI -> FastAPI: Ollama LLM call
FastAPI --> App: Coach response
App -> User: Show chat reply

@enduml
